edward j mathias  the carlyle group skip to main navigation search team edward j mathias location washington dc edward j mathias is a managing director of the carlyle group and a member of the firms board of directors prior to joining carlyle in january  mr mathias was a longtime member of the management committee and board of directors at t rowe price associates inc a major investment management organization he was instrumental in the founding of the carlyle group and assisted in raising the firms initial capital mr mathias serves as an advisor to senior management and is a member of the investment committees for carlyle growth asia growth european technology and subsaharan africa funds additionally he is actively involved with carlyles broadbased investment strategy and serves in an advisory role for the firms global credit funds  mr mathias holds an mba from the harvard business school and an undergraduate degree from the university of pennsylvania where he currently serves as a trustee emeritus he is a member of the president’s advisory council on doing business in africa the council on foreign relations and the trustees council at the national gallery of art  edward j mathias executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of the carlyle group lp snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile edward j mathias managing director and director of carlyle group management llc the carlyle group lpagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background mr edward j mathias also known as ed is a managing director and director of carlyle group management llc the general partner of the carlyle group lp since may   he is also the managing director of the carlyle group lp and serves as the member of board of directors at the firm mr mathias joined the carlyle group in january  and focuses primarily on technology and venture capital activities mr mathias was instrumental in the founding of the carlyle  group and assisted in raising its initial capital and serves as an advisor to senior management additionally he is actively involved with carlyles broadbased investment strategy he serves as a partner and principal of ovation tv inc he is an investment partner at alfred street partners llc he serves as an executive advisor at the chief leadership institute and as an investment advisor at fairfax partners llc he is an advisor of blackstreet capital management llc he served as an advisor of learnvest inc he served in the united states navy supply corps and as a white house military social aide to president mr lyndon johnson he served as an executive of crosshill financial group inc mr mathias served as a senior advisor at maveron llc prior to this he served as a managing director at t rowe price associates inc from  to  he served as a board member at t rowe price associates inc from  to  he cofounded new enterprise associates mr mathias was a special limited partner in trident capital inc he serves on numerous corporate boards including ovationthe arts network and aether systems inc he serves as a director of ovation tv inc touchtunes corporation and performance acquisition corp he has been a director of endeavor acquisition corp since july  endeavour international acquisition corp since november   grand slam acquisition corp since october   and victory acquisition corp since january   mr mathias serves as a director of triple crown acquisition corp and fullbridge inc mr mathias serves as a member of executive advisory board at fairfax partners llc he serves as a member of advisory board at gold bullion international llc and xl education corp he serves as a member of the executive advisory board at calder capital partners he has been a member of advisory board of odgers berndtson since september   he serves as a member of advisory board of diligence inc diligence london the 